    "description": "<p><span >Using a Ranged Weapon, you can spend <strong >2 AP</strong> and <strong >1 SP</strong> to launch a volley of projectiles.</span></p><p ><span >Choose a point within your Weapon’s range. Make a single <strong >Attack Check </strong>and compare it against the <strong >AD </strong>of all creatures of your choice within 1 Space of the chosen point.</span></p><p ><span ><strong >Attack Hit:</strong> You deal 2 Piercing damage to each creature.</span></p><p></p><p><span ><span ><strong ><span >Technique Enhancements</span></strong></span></span></p><ul ><li ><p><span ><strong >Impairing Volley:</strong> <strong >(1 SP) </strong>Force each creature within the area to make a <strong >Physical Save</strong>.<br ><strong >Failure:</strong> They are  <strong >@UUID[Compendium.dc20rpg.rules.JournalEntry.x06moaa9pWzbdrxB.JournalEntryPage.610e6b3221204f0a]{Impaired} </strong>until the end of your next turn.</span></p></li><li ><span ><strong >Blanket of Arrows:</strong> <strong >(1 SP) </strong>Increase the area to 3 Spaces from the chosen point.</span></li><li ><span ><strong >Line of Arrows:</strong> <strong >(1 SP) </strong>Target any creature occupying a space in a line from you to the chosen point, within your weapon’s range.</span></li></ul>",
